---
layout: base.njk
permalink: /projects/
title: Проекти
description: Реализирани уебсайтове на WebStudio28 — портфолио от проекти за различни бизнеси.
---

<div id="projects-page-wrapper">

    <div id="projects-hero-wrapper">
        <div class="container-custom">
            <div id="projects-hero">
                <h1>Нашите проекти</h1>
                <p>Реални сайтове за реални бизнеси — разгледайте част от работата ни.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container-custom">
        <div id="projects-grid">
            {% for project in projects %}
            {% if project.active %}
            <article class="project-card">
                <a href="/projects/{{ project.slug }}/" class="project-card-image-link">
                    <img src="{{ project.thumbnail }}" alt="{{ project.title }}" loading="lazy" onerror="this.src='/assets/images/projects/placeholder.svg'">
                </a>
                <div class="project-card-body">
                    <h2><a href="/projects/{{ project.slug }}/">{{ project.title }}</a></h2>
                    <p>{{ project.description }}</p>
                    <div class="project-card-actions">
                        <a href="/projects/{{ project.slug }}/" class="project-card-link">Виж детайли</a>
                        <a href="{{ project.link }}" class="project-card-link project-card-link-external" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Към сайта</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </article>
            {% endif %}
            {% endfor %}
        </div>
    </div>

</div>
